    "plan_content": "## Plan Summary\n\n**Bug:** Off-by-one error in `src/utils.ts`, line 7.\n\nThe loop condition reads:\n```typescript\nfor (let i = 0; i < items.length - 1; i++) {   // ❌ skips last item\n```\nIt should be:\n```typescript\nfor (let i = 0; i < items.length; i++) {        // ✅ processes all items\n```\n\nThe `- 1` causes the loop to stop one index short, so the last element is never pushed into `results`.\n\n**Single-line fix** — only `src/utils.ts` needs to change. The tests in `tests/utils.test.ts` are already correct and will all pass once the bug is fixed. No config or test changes required.",
